Atiku, a Correctional Service Officer, had earlier asked for the mattress, before agreeing to her divorce request.
Ahmad, who lives in Badarawa, Kaduna, in April 2022, filed for divorce at a Sharia Court sitting in Magajin Gari, Kaduna State,
Kauai also asked Atiku to give Ahmad N20,000 to enable her to buy a new mattress.
The Judge further ordered Atiku, to pay N80,000 to Ahmad, to enable her to pay the debt she incurred during the period of their marriage.
He adjourned the case until July 25, for a ruling on the divorce application.
Earlier, the respondent, who did not give a reason for seeking divorce told the court that she was ready to return her bride price to Atiku.
Atiku told the court that the mattress belonged to his first wife.
